psi.model

Class PsiPhaseStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • psi.model.PsiPhaseStatistics

  • public class PsiPhaseStatistics
extends java.lang.Object
    Tracks run-time statistics for different phases of the psi computation, such as the elapsed time and the amount of cache hit/miss. It is not strictly required to compute the psi, but provides helpful insights on the correctness/performance of the sdk integration.
